nternet with numerous Awards and honours currently boasts over 8.7 million Instagram followers and this has made her a face to watch all around the business world. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-843796 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MDL_5972.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="421" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MDL_5972.jpg 640w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/MDL_5972-300x197.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"> The partnership between these two powerhouses (Mercy Aigbe x Adelove Shipping) has officially begun with a digital campaign in celebration of the 2020/2021 collections. Spotlighted are the images taken during the contract agreement. The partnership, which has been in the works, was a no-brainer, according to Yemi Mustapha, Adelove Shipping Implementation Manager, who says the brand admired the Actress magnetic energy. “We were drawn to her confidence and fierce ambition as much as her power to hold nothing back”, Yemi says in a press release.  The Nigerian Actress, Mercy Aigbe wrote in an Instagram caption announcing the partnership “Another Bag secured! I am so honored to be part of this Number 1 Nigerian Shipping line @adeloveshipping family as I am taking up a big space on that carpet. Adelove Shipping ships both ways – from USA to Nigeria, and from Nigeria to USA, UK and Canada⁣
